= ffmpeg = =

Chicken scheme egg with bindings for ffmpeg.

Note that for now this egg binds only to a small subset of ffmpeg that
deals with video. It is used for computer vision where video files
have only a single stream and audio is irrelevant.

One day this egg will have documentation.

